            <p class="display-3">Pneumonia Precautions</p>
        </div> <br>
        <div class="col row">
            <h5 class="lh-base">
                Pneumonia can vary in severity. Here are the recommended precautions for each stage of pneumonia:
            </h5>
        </div> <br>
        
        <!-- Mild Pneumonia Precautions -->
        <div class="col row">
            <p class="fs-4 fw-bold">Mild Pneumonia</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col row">
            <h5 class="lh-base">
                <ul>
                    <li>Drink plenty of fluids (mainly water) to thin mucus and clear it from the lungs.</li>
                    <li>Get plenty of rest.</li>
                    <li>Take antibiotics or antiviral medication as instructed by a doctor.</li>
                    <li>Avoid smoking to prevent lung irritation.</li>
                    <li>Use a humidifier to reduce throat irritation.</li>
                    <li>Avoid crowded places to reduce the risk of infections.</li>
                    <li>Boost your immune system with a healthy diet.</li>
                </ul>
            </h5>
        </div> <br>

        <!-- Moderate Pneumonia Precautions -->
        <div class="col row">
            <p class="fs-4 fw-bold">Moderate Pneumonia</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col row">
            <h5 class="lh-base">
                <ul>
                    <li>Attend frequent checkups to monitor progress.</li>
                    <li>Continue taking prescribed antibiotics regularly.</li>
                    <li>Use oxygen therapy if recommended, to monitor and maintain oxygen levels.</li>
                    <li>Avoid strenuous physical activities.</li>
                    <li>Sleep with your head elevated to aid breathing.</li>
                    <li>Maintain good hygiene to prevent further infections.</li>
                    <li>Monitor breathing difficulties and chest pain. Seek medical advice if symptoms worsen.</li>
                </ul>
            </h5>
        </div> <br>

        <!-- Severe Pneumonia Precautions -->
        <div class="col row">
            <p class="fs-4 fw-bold">Severe Pneumonia</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col row">
            <h5 class="lh-base">
                <ul>
                    <li>Seek immediate medical attention for close monitoring and treatment.</li>
                    <li>Ventilator support or oxygen therapy may be needed to aid breathing.</li>
                    <li>Continuous monitoring of heart rate, oxygen levels, and respiratory functions is crucial.</li>
                    <li>Fluid management: Ensure proper hydration and avoid both overhydration and dehydration.</li>
                    <li>Stay in an isolated area to prevent spreading the infection to others.</li>
                    <li>Eat a protein-rich diet to support recovery.</li>
                </ul>
            </h5>
        </div> <br>
